title: DDFP 253: Brady Quinn & Ike Taylor
itunes:title: DDFP 253: Brady Quinn & Ike Taylor
description:
Shek and Rank are joined by former first-round draft pick and free agent quarterback Brady Quinn to discuss waiting in the green room on draft day, recall being part of the "Tebowmania" Broncos team and leave the longest voicemail in #DDFP (and most likely in human) history on A.J. Hawk's phone. Plus, Pittsburgh Steelers cornerback and friend of the show Ike Taylor returns to grade Johnny Manziel's pro potential and react to the Don Sterling fiasco in the NBA. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
